{"tid":219623,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"過來人請分享  如果自己養左好耐嘅寵物死左，會唔會再養另一隻？","createTime":"2017-04-27T10:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T09:58:31.000Z","uid":93674,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"366fe903b1d0e8670a7e70a32119419eba5f5edc","tid":219623,"uid":93674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:40:41.000Z","msg":"如題，自己養左貓貓4年，平時都唔會諗呢d，但成日見到上網有d文章講主人陪寵物度過佢地最後幾個鐘，就好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你地睇住佢地死，會唔會再繼續養，面對下一次親人嘅死亡呢？<br />\n不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n奉上主子照片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b402587cb705f0d4739744f7974db9696d6c26","tid":219623,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:41:47.000Z","msg":"會，想畀冇家嘅動物温暖"},{"pid":"01e9733ee8674df998890f9cba3c41c178897608","tid":219623,"uid":93674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/27/184355_b7d395d4192408b1afa192713f7a78a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F27%2F184355_b7d395d4192408b1afa192713f7a78a7.jpg&h=2794727b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z1U5LCR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ1U5LCR.jpg&h=f3127761&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f44108B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff44108B.jpg&h=8e084b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VTCtQYu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVTCtQYu.jpg&h=26d5a8ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97y8984.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%