<br />\n仲要係領養<br />\n佢上手主人對佢勁差<br />\n屌 直情喊唔出 仆街</blockquote><br />\nrip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一路好走 佢會知道你會好掛住佢 好愛佢的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  加油"},{"pid":"5e1dd1b9d6b90929fc2e80b32981985dafba84bc","tid":219623,"uid":84102,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:59:02.000Z","msg":"唔會 傷唔起 經歷過既就知道有幾痛 望住佢啲相 你知道永遠都無得再抱住佢既時候 眼淚就控制唔到 一諗起佢病既樣 一諗起佢過左身全身硬晒既樣  我知道唔可以再承受多次。 我好掛住你呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ecd913fa9a9afef60a4357d43fb522e5a33ae3","tid":219623,"uid":43651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:04:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會 傷唔起 經歷過既就知道有幾痛 望住佢啲相 你知道永遠都無得再抱住佢既時候 眼淚就控制唔到 一諗起佢病既樣 一諗起佢過左身全身硬晒既樣  我知道唔可以再承受多次。 我好掛住你呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好驚呢日 呢段睇到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a805bc8d2986150a24eedcc5dbd436513eafe8","tid":219623,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:10:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔會 傷唔起 經歷過既就知道有幾痛 望住佢啲相 你知道永遠都無得再抱住佢既時候 眼淚就控制唔到 一諗起佢病既樣 一諗起佢過左身全身硬晒既樣  我知道唔可以再承受多次。 我好掛住你呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好驚呢日 呢段睇到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以要對佢地好啲 我而家都好後悔好後悔以前無多啲陪佢 唉"},{"pid":"3895de911ad89a1d67db810e77c47a011a42f604","tid":219623,"uid":93674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T18:29:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔會 傷唔起 經歷過既就知道有幾痛 望住佢啲相 你知道永遠都無得再抱住佢既時候 眼淚就控制唔到 一諗起佢病既樣 一諗起佢過左身全身硬晒既樣  我知道唔可以再承受多次。 我好掛住你呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都好驚呢日 呢段睇到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以要對佢地好啲 我而家都好後悔好後悔以前無多啲陪佢 唉</blockquote><br />\n感受唔到佢嘅體溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  寵物真係要寵多啲"},{"pid":"630177ceeaea2878a999b7ab7b29df864df561a7","tid":219623,"uid":60875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:02:43.000Z","msg":"養左8，9年了，好擔心呢日既來臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果真係到左.. 我想問身後事應該點算？<br />\n唔想到時喊住search資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b80d81eab6d1e6329a16f4995001196abf85afb","tid":219623,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:07:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>養左8，9年了，好擔心呢日既來臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果真係到左.. 我想問身後事應該點算？<br />\n唔想到時喊住search資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n獨立火化 雖然唔想面對 但佢的確會比你行先一步 生老病死 都係狗狗 貓貓 既一個必經階段 緣份到了始終都要離開 ，好好珍惜每一日同佢一齊既日子啦"},{"pid":"ca2507c0a812984a3d96b1e444d9c2f4df41dcb4","tid":219623,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/28/030951_b7967ac6ff0b6bbe3339a8441d3ff735.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F28%2F030951_b7967ac6ff0b6bbe3339a8441d3ff735.jpg&h=523afe76&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504c76f8773116978bd5ff4ba6553fd8224c2a9c","tid":219623,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:12:13.000Z","msg":"生命如此無奈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d228d945f9f8c6d74786db845ab10d8c94d30a59","tid":219623,"uid":108660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T19:45:11.000Z","msg":"會 但唔會養翻同一個品種或者刻意去搵 順其自然啦只會 因為都唔想取代."},{"pid":"fb71f37bd95ebcc5653fe096769fedf389809c67","tid":219623,"uid":7229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T20:12:21.000Z","msg":"其實根本唔會取代到，隻隻都有唔同性格<br />\n反而同時養多幾隻，到時會冇咁辛苦<br />\n總之對佢地好d, 走個陣自己知道俾左一個幸福既家佢，慶幸相遇，無愧於心就好"},{"pid":"9af4ef237fa1000a22d73c4166678ac8e77116cc","tid":219623,"uid":68766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T20:29:38.000Z","msg":"會繼續養<br />\n養過四隻貓其中三隻已經過左身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每一隻貓走果陣都喊到痴左線<br />\n最印象深刻係一隻21歲嘅貓<br />\n佢係我第一隻接觸嘅貓<br />\n同我一齊長大<br />\n喺獸醫度啪針送佢走果陣喺診所喊到跪低<br />\n但之後都有繼續養<br />\n每一隻貓都係獨一無二<br />\n唔會話新貓取代到舊貓"}]}